    </p>
    <p>
        <code>Tooltip</code> is enabled in this example. To see the tooltip in action, hover over a point or tap on a point in touch-enabled devices.
    </p>
    <p>
        More information about the histogram series can be found in this
        <a target="_blank" href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/chart/chart-types/histogram" aria-label="Navigate to the documentation for histogram in ASP.NET Core Chart control">documentation section</a>.
    </p>
}
